  "name": "Morrison COU2 — VAD hemolysis credibility assessment (MRL 3, W-EP-04)",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for CFD hemolysis prediction of the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under ventricular assist device (VAD) conditions. Model Risk Level is set to 3. Seven factors are assessed with full requiredLevel and achievedLevel data; three factors are marked not-assessed with rationale citing scope limitations. The not-assessed factors at MRL 3 constitute an epistemic gap that materially weakens credibility (W-EP-04). Decision is recorded as Accepted despite the unassessed factors, which is the targeted subtle flaw.",
