    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "The credibility assessment team reviewed the seven assessed factors and noted that the majority of assessed factors achieved levels at or near the required levels for MRL 3. The three not-assessed factors (numerical solver error, use error, model form) were considered beyond the scope of the current submission cycle and were deferred without formal justification of their materiality at MRL 3. The team concluded that the assessed evidence was sufficient to support an Accepted decision for the VAD hemolysis COU, subject to future reassessment of the deferred factors.",
